?? JSObject

  • ???????:
    AbstractJSObject, ScriptObjectMirror

    public interface JSObject
    This interface can be implemented by an arbitrary Java class. Nashorn will treat objects of such classes just like nashorn script objects. Usual nashorn operations like obj[i], obj.foo, obj.func(), delete obj.foo will be glued to appropriate method call of this interface.
